data.description: Charming, elegant, and refined, five bedroom, 3.5 bath home located in the prestigious community of Savannah Highlands.. Offering over 4,000 square feet, this home truly has it all. Enjoy a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and center island. The main floor features an open concept including the great room, kitchen, and breakfast nook--which opens out to the patio.  Also find a loft, study, media room, two car garage and beautiful formal dining room--ideal for entertaining. The luxurious master suite boasts his and her closets, en-suite bath with soaking tub, sitting area and bonus room. The new and sophisticated community of Savannah Highlands offers premium amenities, and  is conveniently located just minutes to all downtown Savannah has to offer.
